 WHAT is the best way to rock the season without wrist watches? Wrist bangles to the rescue! Fashionistas and celebs are now rocking wrist bangles. It’s a look that is elegant whether it’s for a casual cocktail bash or a formal event. This is one of the reasons timeless fashion pieces retain their popularity. They go with most things in your wardrobe and transcend the trends. bangles have earned their place as a classic. They change in accordance with season. Before now, thinning silver and gold bangles were must-haves, but big and bold ones, especially strand-cuff, steel and wooden bangles have swept away all other brands of wrist ornament.